trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""></xref> exception block of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_try/catch" name="try/catch" href=""></xref> statement.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""> </xref> unntaksblokk med en <xref uid="langword_csharp_try/catch" name="try/catch" href=""> </xref> setningen.

trans-unit.source: CodeCatchClause can be used to represent a `catch` exception block of a `try/catch` statement.
trans-unit.target: CodeCatchClause kan brukes til å representere en `catch` unntaksblokk med en `try/catch` setningen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.CatchExceptionType%2A> property specifies the type of exception to catch.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.CatchExceptionType%2A>egenskapen angir typen unntak å fange opp.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.CatchExceptionType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.LocalName%2A> property specifies a name for the variable representing the exception that has been caught.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.LocalName%2A>egenskapen angir et navn for variabelen som representerer unntak er mottatt.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.LocalName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.Statements%2A> collection property contains the statements for the `catch` block.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.Statements%2A>egenskapen samlingen inneholder setninger for den `catch` block.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause.Statements%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"></xref> class using the specified local variable name for the exception.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det angitte lokale variabelnavnet for unntaket.

trans-unit.source: The name of the local variable declared in the catch clause for the exception.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den lokale variabelen deklarert i catch-setning for unntaket.

trans-unit.source: This is optional.
trans-unit.target: Dette er valgfritt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"></xref> class using the specified local variable name for the exception and exception type.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det angitte lokale variabelnavnet for unntak og Unntakstype.

trans-unit.source: The name of the local variable declared in the catch clause for the exception.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den lokale variabelen deklarert i catch-setning for unntaket.

trans-unit.source: This is optional.
trans-unit.target: Dette er valgfritt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the type of exception to catch.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir hvilken type unntak å fange opp.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"></xref> class using the specified local variable name for the exception, exception type and statement collection.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeCatchClause"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det lokale variabelen med det angitte navnet for unntaket, unntak type og setningen samling.

trans-unit.source: The name of the local variable declared in the catch clause for the exception.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den lokale variabelen deklarert i catch-setning for unntaket.

trans-unit.source: This is optional.
trans-unit.target: Dette er valgfritt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the type of exception to catch.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir hvilken type unntak å fange opp.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatement"></xref> objects that represent the contents of the catch block.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatement"> </xref> objekter som representerer innholdet i catch-blokk.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of the exception to handle with the catch block.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir typen unntak å håndtere catch-blokk.

trans-unit.source: If a value for this property is not specified, the value of this property defaults to <xref:System.Exception>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en verdi for denne egenskapen ikke er angitt, brukes verdi for denne egenskapen <xref:System.Exception>.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the type of the exception to handle.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir hvilken type unntaket til å håndtere.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the variable name of the exception that the <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""></xref> clause handles.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir variabelnavnet av unntaket som den <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""> </xref> setningsdelen referanser.

trans-unit.source: This property specifies the name of the local variable for the exception.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir navnet på den lokale variabelen for unntaket.

trans-unit.source: This local variable is optional.
trans-unit.target: Denne lokale variabelen er valgfrie.

trans-unit.source: By default, the clause does not have this variable.
trans-unit.target: Som standard har setningsdelen ikke denne variabelen.

trans-unit.source: The name for the exception variable that the <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""></xref> clause handles.
trans-unit.target: Navnet for variabelen unntak som den <xref uid="langword_csharp_catch" name="catch" href=""> </xref> setningsdelen referanser.

trans-unit.source: Gets the statements within the catch block.
trans-unit.target: Henter setninger i catch-blokk.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatementCollection"></xref> containing the statements within the catch block.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatementCollection"> </xref> som inneholder setninger i catch-blokk.
